续应下调 PKM-style routed-expert 方向优先级，而不是继续细扫这条线。"],"notes_to_memory":["已实际落盘新 family `product_key_expert_jumprelu`，修改位于 `sparsify/config.py`、`sparsify/sparse_coder.py`，并补了 `research/AutoResearch/override_registry.py` 的 architecture allowlist。","`product_key_expert_jumprelu` 的结构语义是“learned left/right product-key router + routed static expert sublibraries + expert-local JumpReLU gating”；它不是 `factorized_router_expert_topk` 的重命名，因为 expert logits 来自 pairwise compositional addressing，而不是 low-rank hidden 到 full expert logits。","本地 exact architecture smoke 已通过：`SparseCoderConfig(architecture='product_key_expert_jumprelu', k=32, expansion_factor=1, num_experts=128, active_experts=2, latents_per_expert=192)` 可成功 instantiate、forward、backward。","本地 exact 成本复核：selection_accesses=416768、deployment_accesses=163840、combined_accesses=580608、exact total_cost_ratio=0.138427734375；相对 r235 的 0.160000 释放约 0.02157 objective 空间。","override allowlist 自检已通过：`validate_env_overrides([{key:'ARCHITECTURE',value:'product_key_expert_jumprelu'}], fallback_architecture='expert_jumprelu')` 返回空列表；携带 `NUM_EXPERTS/ACTIVE_EXPERTS/LATENTS_PER_EXPERT/JUMPRELU_INIT_THRESHOLD` 的 family-key 组合校验也返回空列表。"],"reference_round":235,"self_review":"这轮满足单变量原则：运行动作相对 r235 只改 `ARCHITECTURE`。之所以值得做代码原型而不是继续在 `expert_jumprelu` 上微调，是因为 current-target 上现有 matched K=32 probes 已基本把 shared/coarse、factorized-router、hash-router、lowrank-trunk 等相邻结构槽位裁了一遍，而 PKM-style compositional routing 仍是 prompt 明确点名、且与已有 family 不同的新槽位。代码改动保持在最小范围，没有引入新 env key；新增 family 复用了已有 `NUM_EXPERTS/ACTIVE_EXPERTS/LATENTS_PER_EXPERT/JUMPRELU_*` 语义，并完成 whitelist、dispatch、allowlist、smoke 的闭环。主要风险是 product-key 的可分解 expert logits 仍可能像 hash/factorized router 一样伤害选择质量；但这正是当前最值得被干净回答的问题。","summary":"已落盘并自检新的 `product_key_expert_jumprelu` 原型。建议以 r235 为 reference，只改 `ARCHITECTURE=product_key_expert_jumprelu`，做一轮 PKM-style matched architecture probe，直接判断 compositional coarse-to-fine expert routing 能否在 0.1384x 的更低总成本下保住足够的 exceed 表现。","touched_files":["research/AutoResearch/override_registry.py","sparsify/config.py","sparsify/sparse_coder.py"]}

